spec_data.Name: drupal7-xmlsitemap
spec_data.Description:
The XML sitemap module creates a sitemap
that conforms to the sitemaps.org specification.
This helps search engines to more intelligently crawl a website
and keep their results up to date.
The sitemap created by the module can be automatically submitted to Ask,
Google, Bing (formerly Windows Live Search), and Yahoo! search engines.
The module also comes with several submodules
that can add sitemap links for content,
menu items, taxonomy terms, and user profiles.

This package provides the following Drupal module(s):
* xmlsitemap
